high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the stove, and then turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the plum from the sink.
Turn right and walk towards the fridge on your left.
Place the plum on the top shelf inside the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn left, walk towards the white table, and then turn right to face the small black table.
Place the plum to the right of the egg on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool plum on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the sink on the right.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Bring the potato to the fridge on the right.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Bring the potato to the small black table on to the left of the sink.
Put the chilled potato on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the small black table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk a few feet, then turn right and walk up to the sink
Pick up the potato from the sink
Turn right and walk to the fridge
Put the potato in the fridge then remove it
Turn left and walk over to the small dark table left of the kitchen counter
Put the potato on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled potato on the small table
